{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1349,"text":"Can you imagine what the word\n\"TED\" would have looked like"},{"time":4175,"text":"if it had existed during the Roman Empire?"},{"time":8337,"text":"I think maybe something like this."},{"time":11530,"text":"An artisan would have spent days\nin the sun chiseling it into stone."},{"time":19063,"text":"And in the Middle Ages?"},{"time":22975,"text":"A monk, locked in his room,"},{"time":26869,"text":"would write T-E-D with his pen."},{"time":33588,"text":"And without going so far back in time,"},{"time":35457,"text":"how would these letters\nhave looked in the 80s?"},{"time":41358,"text":"They would have had\nelectric, strange colors,"},{"time":44560,"text":"just like our hairstyles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46251,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48612,"text":"If this event were about children,"},{"time":52689,"text":"I would draw the letters like this,"},{"time":55482,"text":"as if they were building blocks,"},{"time":58835,"text":"in vivid colors."},{"time":60498,"text":"And if it were about superheroes instead?"},{"time":64470,"text":"I would do them like this,"},{"time":66044,"text":"inspired by -- in my opinion --\nthe greatest of all:"},{"time":69979,"text":"Superman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71557,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":73075,"text":"The shapes of these letters talk."},{"time":77219,"text":"They tell us things\nbeyond what they represent."},{"time":81751,"text":"They send us to different eras,"},{"time":83883,"text":"they convey values,"},{"time":85909,"text":"they tell us stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90481,"text":"If we think about it,\nour days are full of letters."},{"time":93596,"text":"We see them on the front of the bus,"},{"time":95656,"text":"on the bakery's facade,"},{"time":97902,"text":"on the keyboard we write on,"},{"time":99865,"text":"on our cell phones --"},{"time":101632,"text":"everywhere."},{"time":104566,"text":"Since the beginning of history,"},{"time":106096,"text":"people have felt the need\nto give language an image."},{"time":109439,"text":"And rightly so,"},{"time":111119,"text":"because language is the most important\ncommunication tool we have."},{"time":116984,"text":"Without understanding what a word means,"},{"time":119530,"text":"we can see certain things it conveys."},{"time":123572,"text":"Some letters tell us\nthat something is modern --"},{"time":125905,"text":"at least it was back in the 70s."},{"time":130625,"text":"Others verify the importance\nand monumentality of a place,"},{"time":135071,"text":"and they do so in uppercase."},{"time":137298,"text":"There are letters not made to last long --"},{"time":140253,"text":"and neither is the opportunity\nthey communicate."},{"time":144067,"text":"And there are letters made\nby inexperienced hands"},{"time":147451,"text":"that, whether they mean to or not,"},{"time":149174,"text":"make us imagine\nwhat a place looks like inside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153381,"text":"When I moved to Berlin,\nI experienced firsthand"},{"time":156848,"text":"all the impact that drawn letters\ncan have in our day-to-day life."},{"time":162679,"text":"I arrived in a new city, which was\nexciting and novel for me."},{"time":166207,"text":"Now, dealing with an unfamiliar language\nwas at times very frustrating"},{"time":172932,"text":"and uncomfortable."},{"time":174369,"text":"I found myself several times at parties\nclutching my glass of wine,"},{"time":179103,"text":"without understanding a single word\nof what was being said around me."},{"time":185214,"text":"And of course, I'd smile\nas if I understood everything."},{"time":190386,"text":"I felt limited in my ability\nto say what I thought,"},{"time":195179,"text":"what I felt,"},{"time":197802,"text":"what I believed."},{"time":201316,"text":"Not only did I not understand\nthe conversations,"},{"time":203611,"text":"but the streets were full of signs\nand text that I couldn't read."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209441,"text":"But the shapes of the letters\ngave me clues;"},{"time":214104,"text":"they would open up a little window"},{"time":216561,"text":"to understanding the stories\nenclosed in those shapes."},{"time":222365,"text":"I recognized places\nwhere tradition was important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225293,"text":"[Bakery Pastries Café Restaurant]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227764,"text":"Or I'd know when someone\nwas trying to give me a signal,"},{"time":230661,"text":"and my gut would tell me\nit was better to stay away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233624,"text":"[No trespassing!]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":235430,"text":"I could also tell when something\nwas made to last forever."},{"time":238307,"text":"The shapes of letters helped me\nunderstand my surroundings better"},{"time":241652,"text":"and navigate the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243563,"text":"I was in Paris recently,"},{"time":245493,"text":"and something similar happened to me."},{"time":247709,"text":"After a few days in the city,"},{"time":249832,"text":"I was on the lookout for something\ntasty to take back home."},{"time":253433,"text":"So I walked and walked and walked\nuntil I found the perfect bakery."},{"time":259132,"text":"The sign said it all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260793,"text":"[Bakery]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":262468,"text":"I see it, and even today,\nI imagine the master baker"},{"time":265591,"text":"dedicating the same amount of time\nto each loaf of bread"},{"time":268527,"text":"that the craftsman dedicated\nto each letter of this word."},{"time":272451,"text":"I can see the bread,\nwith just the right ingredients,"},{"time":276230,"text":"being kneaded softly and carefully,"},{"time":278712,"text":"in the same way the craftsman\ndrew the ends of the letters"},{"time":282840,"text":"with smooth and precise curves."},{"time":286565,"text":"I see the master baker placing\nthe buns over a thin layer of flour"},{"time":291712,"text":"so the bottoms don't burn."},{"time":293688,"text":"I think of the craftsman putting\nthe mosaics in the oven one by one,"},{"time":298807,"text":"being careful to not let the ink run."},{"time":302541,"text":"The love for detail\nthat the master baker has"},{"time":306027,"text":"is reflected in the attention\nthat went into creating this sign."},{"time":311746,"text":"Without having tried their bread,\nwe already imagine it tastes good."},{"time":316301,"text":"And I can vouch for it; it was delicious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321200,"text":"I'm a letterer; that's my job --"},{"time":324660,"text":"to draw letters."},{"time":327328,"text":"Just like when you make bread,\nit requires care in its preparation,"},{"time":331438,"text":"just the right amount of ingredients"},{"time":333985,"text":"and love for the details."},{"time":336585,"text":"Our alphabet is at the same time\nmy raw material and my limitation."},{"time":341251,"text":"The basic structure of the letters\nis for me a playing field,"},{"time":344548,"text":"where the only rule is that the reader,\nat the end of the road,"},{"time":349364,"text":"will be able to read the message."},{"time":352270,"text":"Let me show you how I work,"},{"time":354827,"text":"how I \"knead my bread.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":358388,"text":"A while back, I was commissioned\nto design the cover of a classic book,"},{"time":362980,"text":"\"Alice in Wonderland.\""},{"time":366016,"text":"Alice falls in a burrow"},{"time":367763,"text":"and begins an absurd journey\nthrough a world of fantasy, remember?"},{"time":372415,"text":"In this situation, the title of the story\nis my raw material."},{"time":379046,"text":"At first glance, there are elements\nthat are not very important,"},{"time":382364,"text":"and I can decide to make them smaller."},{"time":384272,"text":"For example, I'll write \"in\"\non a smaller scale."},{"time":389330,"text":"Then I'll try some other ideas."},{"time":391273,"text":"What if, to communicate\nthe idea of \"wonder,\""},{"time":393858,"text":"I used my best handwriting,"},{"time":396950,"text":"with lots of curleycues here and there?"},{"time":400960,"text":"Or what if I focused more on the fact\nthat the book is a classic"},{"time":404745,"text":"and used more conventional lettering,"},{"time":408118,"text":"making everything look\na little more stiff and serious,"},{"time":412022,"text":"like in an encyclopedia or old books?"},{"time":416847,"text":"Or how would it look, considering\nthis book has so much gibberish,"},{"time":421743,"text":"if I combined both universes\nin a single arrangement:"},{"time":426378,"text":"rigid letters and smooth letters\nliving together in the same composition."},{"time":433496,"text":"I like this idea,\nand I'll work on it in detail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438033,"text":"I use another sheet of paper\nto work more comfortably."},{"time":442580,"text":"I mark some guidelines,"},{"time":444776,"text":"delimiting the framework\nwhere the words will be."},{"time":449923,"text":"There, I can start giving\nform to each letter."},{"time":452572,"text":"I work carefully."},{"time":454638,"text":"I dedicate time to each letter\nwithout losing sight of the whole."},{"time":459974,"text":"I draw the ends\nof the letters methodically."},{"time":463450,"text":"Are they square or round?"},{"time":466986,"text":"Are they pointy or plump and smooth?"},{"time":472213,"text":"I always make several sketches,"},{"time":473851,"text":"where I'll try different ideas\nor change elements."},{"time":478459,"text":"And there comes a point when\nthe drawing turns into precise forms,"},{"time":482930,"text":"with colors, volumes\nand decorative elements."},{"time":487783,"text":"Alice, the celebrity here,\nis placed at the front"},{"time":491113,"text":"with volume in her letters."},{"time":493545,"text":"Lots of points and lines\nplaying in the background"},{"time":496767,"text":"help me convey that in this story,\nlots of things happen."},{"time":500724,"text":"And it helps to represent\nthe feeling it generates,"},{"time":503173,"text":"as if you had your head in the clouds."},{"time":506780,"text":"And of course, there's Alice,\nlooking at her wonderland."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515444,"text":"Drawing the letters of this title,\nI recreate the text's atmosphere a little."},{"time":521660,"text":"I let the reader see the story\nthrough a peephole in the door."},{"time":526681,"text":"To do that, I gave shape\nto concepts and ideas"},{"time":529205,"text":"that already exist in our imagination:"},{"time":532047,"text":"the idea of dreams,"},{"time":534148,"text":"of chaos,"},{"time":535802,"text":"the concept of wonder."},{"time":540284,"text":"The typography and the shape of letters\nwork a bit like gestures"},{"time":545049,"text":"and tone of voice."},{"time":546817,"text":"It's not the same to say,"},{"time":549541,"text":"(In a flat tone of voice)\n\"TEDxRíodelaPlata's audience is huge,\""},{"time":552885,"text":"as it is to say (In an animated voice),\n\"TEDxRíodelaPlata's audience is huge!\""},{"time":559713,"text":"Gestures and tone are part of the message."},{"time":564700,"text":"By giving shape to the letters,"},{"time":566714,"text":"I can decide more precisely\nwhat I mean to say and how,"},{"time":570726,"text":"beyond the literal text."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575397,"text":"I can say my favorite swear word\nin a very flowery way"},{"time":581801,"text":"and be really corny\nwhen I talk about love."},{"time":586541,"text":"I can talk loudly and in a grandiose way"},{"time":591899,"text":"or in a soft and poetic voice."},{"time":597581,"text":"And I can communicate the difference\nbetween Buenos Aires"},{"time":603275,"text":"and Berlin,"},{"time":606700,"text":"two cities I know very well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611089,"text":"It was precisely in Berlin\nwhere my work became more colorful,"},{"time":615809,"text":"more expressive,"},{"time":618008,"text":"more precise at telling stories."},{"time":621441,"text":"Everything I couldn't say\nat those parties,"},{"time":624103,"text":"standing there holding my glass of wine,"},{"time":626877,"text":"exploded in shapes and colors on paper."},{"time":632379,"text":"Without my realizing it,\nthis limitation that language has"},{"time":635881,"text":"became an engine"},{"time":637910,"text":"that propelled me to perfect the tools\nwith which I could express myself."},{"time":643672,"text":"If I couldn't say it by speaking,"},{"time":646164,"text":"this was my way of talking"},{"time":649155,"text":"and telling things to the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653398,"text":"Since then, my big quest\nhas been to find my own voice"},{"time":657560,"text":"and to tell stories with the exact\ntone and gesture I want."},{"time":663957,"text":"No more, no less."},{"time":667860,"text":"That's why I combine colors,"},{"time":671487,"text":"textures"},{"time":673026,"text":"and of course, letters,"},{"time":676632,"text":"which are the heart."},{"time":679183,"text":"And that's why I always want them to have\nshapes that are truly beautiful"},{"time":684435,"text":"and exquisite."},{"time":686879,"text":"Telling stories by drawing letters --"},{"time":689607,"text":"that's my job."},{"time":692501,"text":"And with that I look for\na reaction in the reader,"},{"time":694896,"text":"to wake them up somehow,"},{"time":697272,"text":"to make them dream,"},{"time":699109,"text":"make them feel moved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":702203,"text":"I believe that\nif the message is important,"},{"time":705279,"text":"it requires work and craftsmanship."},{"time":708314,"text":"And if the reader is important,"},{"time":711365,"text":"they deserve beauty and fantasy as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715714,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}